11#include <arm_neon.h>
12
13#include "./vp8_rtcd.h"
14#include "vp8/common/blockd.h"
15
16void vp8_dequantize_b_neon(BLOCKD *d, short *DQC) {
17 int16x8x2_t qQ, qDQC, qDQ;
18
19 qQ = vld2q_s16(d->qcoeff);
20 qDQC = vld2q_s16(DQC);
21
22 qDQ.val[0] = vmulq_s16(qQ.val[0], qDQC.val[0]);
23 qDQ.val[1] = vmulq_s16(qQ.val[1], qDQC.val[1]);
24
25 vst2q_s16(d->dqcoeff, qDQ);
26}
